{SECT 0 {PARA 256 "" 0 "" {TEXT 257 23 "Algebraic Manipulations" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 14 "Lisa Alexander" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 7 "4-11-03" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 57 "Save your current worksheet as work02-yourlastname.mws.  \+
" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 531 "1.  \+
Basic Manipulations.  We can use Maple to manipulate algebraic express
ion as well as to perform arithmetic calculations.  The intent is to l
earn some basic Maple syntax, while observing some of the neat feature
s of a Computer Algebra System (CAS).  We will also review some basic \+
concepts from arithmetic.   Perform the following calculations with Ma
ple.  As you do these exercises enter notes and comments onto your wor
ksheet in text mode.  Note the usage of operators +,-,*,/,^,!  and the
 usage or non-usage of parentheses.  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "
" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 60 "Let the following variables represent
 algebraic expressions:" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 
0 "" {TEXT -1 2 "  " }{MPLTEXT 1 0 16 "f := x^3-x^2-2*x" }{TEXT -1 11 
"      2.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "g := 6*x^3+11*x^2+6*x+1" "6#>%\"gG,**&\"
\"'\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"$F(F(*&\"#6F(*$F*\"\"#F(F(*&F'F(F*F(F(F(F(" }
{TEXT -1 22 "                 3.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "h := x^3-5*x+x^2-
5;" "6#>%\"hG,**$%\"xG\"\"$\"\"\"*&\"\"&F)F'F)!\"\"*$F'\"\"#F)F+F," }
{TEXT -1 19 "                   " }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 
1 0 0 "" }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "4.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "F := x
^4-1" "6#>%\"FG,&*$%\"xG\"\"%\"\"\"F)!\"\"" }{TEXT -1 22 "            \+
    5.    " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "G := 3*x^4+4*x^3-2*x^2+x-6;" "6#>%\"GG,,*&
\"\"$\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"%F(F(*&F+F(*$F*F'F(F(*&\"\"#F(*$F*F/F(!\"\"F*F(
\"\"'F1" }{TEXT -1 14 "         6.   " }{XPPEDIT 19 1 "H := 2*x^2+3*x-
2" "6#>%\"HG,(*&\"\"#\"\"\"*$%\"xGF'F(F(*&\"\"$F(F*F(F(F'!\"\"" }
{TEXT -1 24 "                        " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "
